            "jpName": "ビューティー安心沢",
            "enName": "Beauty Anshinzawa",
            "jpText": "……ンンン、なるほどね～♪\r\nいいわよいいわよォ～！",
            "enText": "…Hmmm, very good!♪ What a lovely vow, my dear!",
