        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "アタシは、カワカミのようにハッキリとした夢はないけれど\r\n……それでも、なりたい自分がいるんです。",
            "enText": "I don't have a clear dream like Kawakami… but I do want \nto become a better version of myself.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 271,
            "voiceIdx": 19,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -1507792472373485393
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5287405937393648581,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "自分が誇れる自分になって、堂々とレースを走りたい。\r\nどんな子とも全力で競い合えるようになりたい。",
            "enText": "I want to be proud of myself and run my races \nwith confidence. I want to be able to do my very \nbest against every opponent I meet.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 241,
            "voiceIdx": 20,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -7290830774949944325
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1038706737226249922,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "尊敬する先輩やメジロの子たち……誰にも負けない\r\nウマ娘になるために、アタシには勝負服が必要なんです！",
            "enText": "I want to become an undefeatable horsegirl who can stand \nagainst even my role models and other Mejiro members. \nAnd for that, I need my own racewear!",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 257,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 2414865416672508522
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -3286891875102095054
                }
