            "pathId": -6932630171088214796,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビューティー安心沢",
            "enName": "Beauty Anshinzawa",
            "jpText": "ふゥん？",
            "enText": "Hm?",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 49,
            "voiceIdx": 22,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -5173372214106543772
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 1511073787518737140
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2163786740606168577,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "勝負服は、自信が持てないアタシを支えて、\r\n背中を押してくれる存在だから――",
            "enText": "To me, my racewear is an essential presence that supports \nand propels me forward, lacking in confidence as I am.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 201,
            "voiceIdx": 23,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 175,
                    "pathId": 5581068296778987302
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 1461549147540976968
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6074625247403045044,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "今はまだ未熟でも、いつか花開けるように\r\n勝負服と共に歩んでいきたいんです！",
            "enText": "I may still be inexperienced, but I want to walk \nhand in hand with my racewear, so I can bloom \ninto my full potential one day!",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 198,
            "voiceIdx": 24,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -7987704656339232863
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5448658884027309733
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3859485824052781837,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "その……、\r\n誓いというより、願いになってしまいますけど。",
            "enText": "Sorry… That was more of a wish than a vow.",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 203,
            "voiceIdx": 25,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 163,
                    "pathId": 5454322547712229260
